  <section class="problem-section">
    <div class="problem-container">
      <h2 class="reveal">🚨 The Water Crisis We're Solving</h2>
      <p class="subtitle reveal">Real evidence from Tamil Nadu's water bodies showing urgent environmental threats</p>
      <div class="problem-grid">
        <div class="problem-card reveal-left">
          <img src="/images/algae-pollution.jpg" alt="Algae pollution in Coimbatore">
          <div class="problem-content">
            <span class="location-badge">📍 Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu</span>
            <h3>🦠 Excessive Algal Blooms</h3>
            <p>Severe algal bloom pollution caused by excess nutrients and high chlorophyll-a concentrations in local water bodies.</p>
            <p><strong style="color:#e2e8f0;">Environmental Impact:</strong></p>
            <ul class="impact-list">
              <li>🐟 Fish kills — depletes dissolved oxygen</li>
              <li>☠️ Toxic blooms — harmful to wildlife and humans</li>
              <li>💧 Water contamination — unsafe for drinking/irrigation</li>
              <li>🌡️ Ecosystem disruption — blocks sunlight to underwater plants</li>
              <li>⚠️ Health risks — skin, respiratory and GI issues</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card reveal-right">
          <img src="/images/plastic-pollution.jpg" alt="Plastic debris in Coimbatore">
          <div class="problem-content">
            <span class="location-badge">📍 Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu</span>
            <h3>🗑️ Plastic &amp; Solid Waste Pollution</h3>
            <p>Visible plastic debris and solid waste accumulation along riverbanks creating long-term environmental damage.</p>
            <p><strong style="color:#e2e8f0;">Environmental Impact:</strong></p>
            <ul class="impact-list">
              <li>🐢 Wildlife harm — animals ingest or entangle in plastic</li>
              <li>🔬 Microplastics — enter the food chain</li>
              <li>💀 Toxic leaching — contaminates water and soil</li>
              <li>🌊 Waterway blockage — increases flood risk</li>
              <li>🏞️ Habitat destruction — smothers aquatic vegetation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:3rem;padding:2.5rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);border:1px solid rgba(14,165,233,0.15);border-radius:18px;backdrop-filter:blur(12px);" class="reveal">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom:1rem;font-size:1.6rem;color:#e2e8f0;">🎯 Our Monitoring Solution</h3>
        <p style="font-size:1rem;line-height:1.9;max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;color:#94a3b8;">
          R-TECH's autonomous robotic multispectral radiometer system continuously monitors
          <strong style="color:var(--ocean-1);">chlorophyll-a levels, turbidity, plastic signatures, and pH</strong>.
          Our data trains and validates satellite observations from
          <strong style="color:#e2e8f0;">OceanSat-3 OCM and Sentinel-2/3</strong>, providing real-time alerts to authorities for immediate action.
        </p>
